3
00:00:04,540 --> 00:00:08,084
<i>Do you still remember your job description, that you're my secretary?</i>

4
00:00:08,084 --> 00:00:09,306
<i>Can you not go?</i>

5
00:00:09,306 --> 00:00:12,630
<i>Boss, I don't want to go back on my words with the client.</i>

6
00:00:12,630 --> 00:00:16,100
