262
00:26:06,063 --> 00:26:08,360
What are you peeping at?

263
00:26:11,250 --> 00:26:15,500
Since you're sick, wouldn't it be better if you wore a shirt?

264
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:18,550
Why?

265
00:26:21,100 --> 00:26:22,746
Here!

266
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:29,680
