278
00:27:49,065 --> 00:27:50,903
I am resting, though.

279
00:27:50,903 --> 00:27:54,415
You're not. You're working.

280
00:27:56,360 --> 00:27:58,674
It's not a big deal.

281
00:28:00,737 --> 00:28:03,078
You're so stubborn.

282
00:28:04,370 --> 00:28:08,094
Have you eaten and taken your medicine?

283
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,615
