290
00:29:01,541 --> 00:29:06,715
Nezumi. Nezumi, wait!

291
00:29:13,455 --> 00:29:18,505
Nezumi-san, may I kiss you?

292
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:27,565
If you don't answer, I might take that as a yes.

293
00:29:55,210 --> 00:29:57,265
Nezumi-san,

294
00:29:59,629 --> 00:30:01,411
get up.

295
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:05,205
I will get up!

296
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:11,626
