297
00:30:15,194 --> 00:30:17,112
Yes.

298
00:30:17,112 --> 00:30:19,634
Can you tell me why?

299
00:30:25,131 --> 00:30:28,217
I feel like I'm not suitable for the company.

300
00:30:28,946 --> 00:30:32,600
