301
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:40,940
but I have been asked to do many other things.

302
00:30:41,692 --> 00:30:46,131
When you do something you're not good at, you often make mistakes.

303
00:30:47,697 --> 00:30:51,172
Like with matters regarding Khun Mark and P'Ploy.

304
00:30:52,234 --> 00:30:56,325
