309
00:31:15,650 --> 00:31:18,775
People will stop talking after a while.

310
00:31:18,775 --> 00:31:21,542
I chose you to work with me

311
00:31:21,542 --> 00:31:26,112
because I see that you have better skills and attitude than the others.

312
00:31:26,865 --> 00:31:30,860
I may not have told you,

313
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:33,880
