315
00:31:45,095 --> 00:31:49,028
Are you sick? Did you catch it from me?

316
00:31:49,028 --> 00:31:51,060
That's not it.

317
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:57,760
It's my habit. When I'm nervous, I like to do it.

318
00:31:57,760 --> 00:31:59,765
It's strange, isn't it?

319
00:32:01,470 --> 00:32:05,365
Not at all. It's cute.

320
00:32:06,610 --> 00:32:10,750
♫ <i>Then please take responsibility</i> ♫

321
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:19,060
♫ <i>You make me confused about you, I don't want this</i> ♫

322
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:23,439
So you're not going to quit anymore, right?

323
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:29,580
Right.

324
00:32:32,214 --> 00:32:34,419
Is there anything else you want to tell me?

325
00:32:36,545 --> 00:32:39,269
Actually, there's one thing.

326
00:32:42,815 --> 00:32:45,392
About Khun Mark?

327
00:32:45,392 --> 00:32:51,540
You're still angry that I spoke to you harshly that day

328
00:32:51,540 --> 00:32:54,100
when you were with Khun Mark, right?

329
00:32:56,337 --> 00:32:58,705
About that day,

330
00:32:58,705 --> 00:33:00,579
I'm sorry.

331
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:08,431
I was just... angry.

332
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:13,092
I don't like seeing you with another guy,

333
00:33:13,092 --> 00:33:15,585
so I acted idiotically.

334
00:33:19,182 --> 00:33:21,310
This is not about that.

335
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,910
Oh?

336
00:33:25,937 --> 00:33:31,120
