434
00:45:12,709 --> 00:45:16,459
Of course, we do. She's our boss from headquarters.

435
00:45:16,459 --> 00:45:21,120
She's the reason we earn enough for a living today.

436
00:45:21,120 --> 00:45:26,365
She's pretty, rich, smart, and kind.

437
00:45:26,365 --> 00:45:30,112
How many times will I need to be reborn to be like her?

438
00:45:30,112 --> 00:45:33,131
I really want to be born as Rena-san.

439
00:45:33,131 --> 00:45:34,863
I know what you're planning.

440
00:45:34,863 --> 00:45:39,432
