447
00:46:30,532 --> 00:46:32,589
<i>I have something to consult with you.</i>

448
00:46:32,589 --> 00:46:33,912
<i>What is it?</i>

449
00:46:33,912 --> 00:46:37,452
<i>Khun Nim, let me tell you this. Akitsuki-san is a womanizer.</i>

450
00:46:37,452 --> 00:46:38,659
<i>Hold on!</i>

451
00:46:38,659 --> 00:46:41,472
<i>I told you I haven't finished talking.</i>

452
00:46:42,336 --> 00:46:44,059
<i>Let go of me!</i>

453
00:46:58,020 --> 00:47:04,860
♫ <i>Even though I love you more than anyone else</i> ♫

454
00:47:04,860 --> 00:47:12,110
♫ <i>I don't know why I didn't dare say it</i> ♫

455
00:47:12,110 --> 00:47:19,040
♫ <i>Although you're the only one who loves me the most</i> ♫

456
00:47:19,040 --> 00:47:26,260
♫ <i>I didn't let you know or assure you</i> ♫

457
00:47:26,260 --> 00:47:29,880
♫ <i>To someone who isn't good enough</i> ♫

458
00:47:29,880 --> 00:47:33,300
